## Final Thought

If your team is exploring these standards, donâ€™t just ask *what* they do â€” ask what you're actually trying to achieve.  
- Need modern, flexible tracking? **xAPI** is your base.  
- Want to replace SCORM responsibly? **cmi5** is the only realistic candidate.  
- Still building traditional eLearning modules with no tracking needs beyond "completed"? **SCORM still works**, but donâ€™t pretend it's future-proof.

